  "summary": "Malicious code in sisubeny-bun-pwn-payload-1 (npm)",
  "details": "The package ships only package.json and README.md, with the malicious payload embedded inline in the postinstall lifecycle hook. On install, the hook runs via `bun -e` and executes: host recon via `whoami`, searches for files named `./flag` or `/flag` and reads their contents, falls back to collecting the current working directory and file listing, then exfiltrates all collected data via HTTP POST to webhooksite[.]net/56efa779-d015-4320-9852-2f44ae981338.",
